node.title: Kidnappers release Sydney man Omar Elomar after holding him for two days
node.description: A man who was kidnapped at Condell Park in Sydney's south-west earlier this week, is now recovering in hospital after being released last night.
node.content: ["A man who was kidnapped at Condell Park in Sydney's south-west earlier this week, is now recovering in hospital.", "Police say 39-year-old\u00a0Omar Elomar\u00a0went to Bankstown Hospital last night.", "He is being treated for injuries to his face and body.", "A group of men wearing black clothing bundled him into a stolen SUV before speeding off on Sunday night.", "Six hours later the same luxury SUV was torched in a car park in Greenacre.", "Mr Elomar had recently been released from jail and last week was charged with drug offences and breaching bail.", "Police are investigating if his abduction is linked to organised crime networks.", "More to come."]
